title: Ep 2464 - Jethalals Nightmare
shortDesc: Jethalal's has a nightmare in which Bhide has unleashed his wrath on him for Sakaram's misfortune. Meanwhile, Taarak is sleepless worried about Bhide's anger when he does not find Sakaram.

title: Ep 2465 - Trouble on a Sunday
shortDesc: Sunday is turning out to be a nightmarish experience for Taarak as he contemplates the consequences when Bhide finds Sakaram missing. Bhide's relatives pay a surprise visit and take Madhvi and Sonu out, leaving Bhide at home.

title: Ep 2466 - Lesson For Laughter
shortDesc: While all the families of Gokuldham Society rejoice and share some laughs. Bhide is still in his comfortable sleep. While the kids are worried about, the consequence of their action. Watch how the story rolls in this episode!

title: Ep 2467 - Bhide in Distress
shortDesc: Bhide is running helter-skelter to find his beloved scooter, Sakaram. Taarak, Jethalal, Sodhi and Hathi try to pacify Bhide. Jethalal comes up with an idea and claims that Popatlal has taken Bhide's scooter at night.

title: Ep 2468 - Bhides Rage
shortDesc: Jethalal instigates Bhide against Popatlal. Iyer is suspicious of Jethalal's claims and follows him to dig out the truth.  Later, when Popatlal arrives, Abdul informs him that Bhide has cursed him.

title: Ep 2469 - Jethalal in Trouble
shortDesc: Popatlal and Bhide engage in a verbal duel. Finally, before things get any worse, Popatlal reveals that he has nothing to do with Sakaram's disappearance.

title: Ep 2470 - Bhides Questions
shortDesc: Bhide's suspicion on Tappu is turning out to be certainly true for him as he finds one clue after the other that points towards the hand of Tappu in Sakara's disappearance.

title: Ep 2471 - Tappus Answers Bhides Questions
shortDesc: Bhide asks Tappu to look into Champaklal's eyes and answer the questions he asks. Tappu manages to hide the fact that he crashed Sakaram. Bhide is now convinced that Sakaram has been stolen.

title: Ep 2472 - The Police Complaint
shortDesc: Jethalal finally reveals to Popatlal about Sakaram's accident. Popatlal promises Jethalal that he will keep the entire incident a secret from Bhide. All is not well as Jethalal contemplates whether to file a police complaint as instructed by Bhide.

title: Ep 2473 - Jethalals Plan
shortDesc: Jethalal returns to Gokuldham without filing a police complaint. Bhide is furious and wants to know the reason. Jethalal uses his wit to divert Bhide's attention to an ascetic, who can find out lost things.

title: Ep 2474 - Nattu Kaka as Tun Baba
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka is getting ready to play the role of Tun Baba in order to help Jethalal cover up Sakaram's accident. Bhide is impatient and wants to meet Tun Baba as soon as possible.

title: Ep 2475 - Nattu Kakas Premonition
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka puts up a show disguised as Tun Baba. The Gokuldham society members believe Tun Baba has magical powers and will find Sakaram. Taarak notices that Nattu Kaka's fake beard is about to fall off. How will Jethalal save the day?

title: Ep 2476 - Tappu Senas Confession
shortDesc: Sakaram finally returns to Gokuldham society. Bhide is overjoyed to see his beloved scooter. Then, Bhide turns to Tappu Sena and apologizes for having suspected their hand in Sakaram's disappearance.

title: Ep 2477 - Bhides Punishment
shortDesc: After hearing Tappu's confession, Champaklal asks Bhide to punish Tappu Sena. Bhide asks Tappu to record his confession and post it on social media.

title: Ep 2478 - Bhides Unusual Calmness
shortDesc: Sonu and Madhvi finally return from their trip and find Bhide in an unusually calm state. Bhide tries to hide the happenings of the day from Madhvi but fails. Madhvi forces Bhide to reveal what happened in Gokuldham in their absence.
